node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Blunts & Blondes on June 15, 2021 tagging @djnittigritti. May be an image of 1 person, smoking and text that says 'NITTI GRITTI X BLUNTS BLONDES THE LOUD'.

node.text: New one dropping this Friday with my boy Nitti Gritti! Get ready for The Loud! 💨
FORBIDDEN KINGDOM VIDEO DUMP! They had to put the tarp up twice because it started pouring so hard but y’all didn’t give a fuck! Thank you so much for an unforgettable set!
